Then the four of us and James' entire extended family that came all the way from LA for an engagement party, hit up the mean streets of NYC. Yesteday, I dropped Sarah off somewhere in the middle of Connecticut to meet her family, and now I am home in MA and am wicked tired, but at the same time, too lazy to go to bed. Anwaysssa, enough of this for now!
